Package net.etfbl.pj2.model

Class TransportVehicle

java.lang.Object
net.etfbl.pj2.model.TransportVehicle
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Chargeable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Car, ElectricBike, ElectricScooter
public abstract class TransportVehicle extends Object implements Chargeable, Serializable
Represents a transport vehicle that can be charged and drained. This is an abstract class that implements the Chargeable interface and is Serializable.

2.6.2024.
